---
---

<section class="MpAbout" id="about">
  <div class="MpAbout__radial"></div>
  <div class="MpAbout__inner">
    <div class="MpAbout__header">
      <div class="MpAbout__titleBg">ABOUT</div>
      <div class="MpAbout__titleCenter">
        <div class="MpAbout__titleAccent"></div>
        <div class="MpAbout__titleGroup">
          <span class="MpAbout__titleEn">ABOUT</span>
          <h2 class="MpAbout__titleJa">プロジェクトについて</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="MpAbout__body">
      <p class="MpAbout__text">
        Victoria Maid Manorは、<br>
        クラシカルな雰囲気の中でゆったりとした時間をお届けするメイド館。
      </p>
      <p class="MpAbout__text">
        紅茶の淹れ方講座や古典の朗読会、ピアノの生演奏から、雑談やゲームまで——<br>
        格式を大切にしながらも、使用人たちの意外な一面が見える配信をお届けしています。
      </p>
      <div class="MpAbout__divider"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
  @use '../../styles/foundation/mixin' as mix;

  .MpAbout {
    background-color: var(--mp-color-bg-warm);
    padding: 112px 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;

    @include mix.mq(sp) {
      padding: 64px 0;
    }

    &__radial {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      width: 500px;
      height: 500px;
      background: radial-gradient(
        circle at center,
        rgba(232, 115, 42, .05) 0%,
        transparent 70%
      );
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    &__inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin-inline: auto;
      padding-inline: 40px;

      @include mix.mq(sp) {
        padding-inline: 20px;
      }
    }

    &__header {
      position: relative;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 64px;

      @include mix.mq(sp) {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
    }

    &__titleBg {
      position: absolute;
      top: -26px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-family: var(--mp-font-main);
      font-size: 6.25rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      color: rgba(232, 115, 42, .05);
      line-height: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
      user-select: none;
      white-space: nowrap;

      @include mix.mq(sp) {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        top: -16px;
      }
    }

    &__titleCenter {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    &__titleAccent {
      width: 40px;
      height: 2px;
      background-color: var(--mp-color-primary);
    }

    &__titleGroup {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    &__titleEn {
      font-size: .6875rem;
      letter-spacing: .25em;
      color: var(--mp-color-primary);
    }

    &__titleJa {
      font-family: var(--mp-font-main);
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      color: var(--mp-color-dark);

      @include mix.mq(sp) {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }
    }

    &__body {
      text-align: center;
    }

    &__text {
      font-size: .875rem;
      line-height: 2.6;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      color: rgba(26, 26, 46, .8);

      & + & {
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      @include mix.mq(sp) {
        font-size: .8125rem;
        line-height: 2.2;

        br {
          display: none;
        }
      }
    }

    &__divider {
      width: 48px;
      height: 1px;
      background-color: rgba(232, 115, 42, .3);
      margin: 40px auto 0;
    }
  }
</style>
